The Inspector-General of Police, Mohammaed Adamu, has blamed the Indigenous People of Biafra (IPOB) for the attacks on the Imo Police Command. In a statement, which CP Frank Mba, Force Public Relations Officer, issued on his behalf, the IGP directed the Commissioner of Police in Imo to carry out holistic investigations into the incident with a view to fishing-out the perpetrators and bringing them to justice. Details laterâ€¦ 